

1-> connect instance to vs code using .pem file
2-> Create new folder use this command 
       mkdir foldername
3->    sudo apt-get update
4->    sudo apt install npm
5->    sudo apt install nginx
6->     cd /etc/nginx/sites-available/
    ->  ls
          default
7->     sudo vi default
        for open insert mode press i
        for close the insert mode press :wq enter
8->    sudo nginx -t
     -> ok
9->     sudo apt-get install nodejs
10->   cd ~
1->    in main folder 
           sudo npm i and start the Server

    if 404 error found in browser 
       -> sudo sustemctl restart nginx